# List of _Jane the Virgin_ episodes

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Jump to: navigation, search

_[Jane the Virgin](/wiki/Jane_the_Virgin "Jane the Virgin")_ is an
[American](/wiki/Television_in_the_United_States "Television in the United
States") comedy-drama television series that premiered on [The
CW](/wiki/The_CW "The CW") on October 13, 2014. The series follows Jane
Villanueva, a hard-working, religious young Latina woman whose vow to save her
virginity until marriage is shattered when a doctor mistakenly [artificially
inseminates](/wiki/Artificial_insemination "Artificial insemination") her
during a checkup. To make matters worse, the biological donor is a married
man, a former playboy and cancer survivor who is not only the new owner of the
hotel where Jane works, but was also her former teenage crush.

The show was ordered to series on May 8, 2014[1], followed by a full season
order on October 21, 2014.[2] On January 11, 2015, the show was renewed for a
second season.[3] On March 11, 2016, the show was renewed for a third
season.[4] On January 8, 2017, the show was renewed for a fourth season[5],
which debuted on October 13, 2017.[6]

As of February 9,
2018,[[update]](//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=List_of_Jane_the_Virgin_episodes&action=edit)
74 episodes of _Jane the Virgin_ have aired.
